		<li><b>Installed - Administrator.</b> Shows the Languages available for the back-end of the web site. See <a href="<?php echo Route::url('index.php?option=com_help&view=help&keyref=Help25:Extensions_Language_Manager_Installed'); ?>" title="Help25:Extensions Language Manager Installed">Installed Languages Help Screen</a></li>
